<p>A heartbeat and silence, yin and yang, light and darkness, life and death—the essence of life lies in the eternal struggle of opposites. “Heart” and “Beat” are two sides of the same coin. By themselves, they are nothing more than two images, indistinguishable from trillions of others. But together, they unlock the sound of a beating heart hidden within.</p>
