<p class="post__lead msg msg--highlight ">In my recent project, I explored the fascinating intersection of sound and image by creating a unique puzzle—a visual and auditory artifact that could only be unlocked through the pairing of a matching image. To add a layer of digital innovation, I realized this concept as a pair of NFTs (Non-Fungible Tokens).</p>
<h4 class="wp-block-heading">What Are NFTs?</h4>
<p>NFTs are unique digital assets stored on a blockc</p>
