<p>hain, representing ownership of a specific item, such as art, music, or collectibles. Unlike cryptocurrencies like Bitcoin, NFTs are non-fungible, meaning each token is distinct and cannot be exchanged on a one-to-one basis. Their uniqueness and traceable ownership make NFTs a revolutionary medium for creators and collectors.</p>
